td>健康之路(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02587:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02587\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02587-HK</a>)</td><td>21.75</td><td>-13.35</td></tr><tr><td>環球醫療(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02666:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02666\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02666-HK</a>)</td><td>5.41</td><td>+3.44</td></tr><tr><td>腦動極光-B(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:06681:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/06681\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">06681-HK</a>)</td><td>6.89</td><td>+0.44</td></tr></table></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　(ed)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
